Since you are only level 10, I'd recommend you play Amumu and Xin Zhao.  They have quite safe jungle clears, are rather straight-forward to play, have flexible build-path (letting them build offensive and defensive items as necessary) and are good gankers.

If you are looking for build paths, I'd probably recommend something along the following lines to begin with:
{{champion:5}} {{item:3111}} {{item:1419}} {{item:3142}}  {{item:3071}}  {{item:3143}}  {{item:3065}}
{{champion:32}} {{item:3020}} {{item:1409}} {{item:3110}} {{item:3102}} {{item:3151}} {{item:3135}} 

Obviously, these are not the be-all end-all build paths for the champions, but they are a decent place to start and decent general builds.
